contents:
[[example]]
name = "multiple_variants"
required-features = [ "thin", "light", "regular", "bold", "fill",]

[package]
name = "egui-phosphor"
description = "Phosphor icons for egui"
version = "0.5.0"
edition = "2021"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
repository = "https://github.com/amPerl/egui-phosphor"

[features]
default = [ "regular",]
thin = []
light = []
regular = []
bold = []
fill = []

[dev-dependencies]
eframe = "0.27"

[dependencies.egui]
version = "0.27"
default-features = false

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/connorslade/egui-phosphor"]
git = "https://github.com/connorslade/egui-phosphor"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/connorslade/misc"]
git = "https://github.com/connorslade/misc"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
